    ///   will return all options contracts. 'in_the_money' will return options
    ///   contracts that are in the money (call options with strike prices below
    ///   the current price, put options with strike prices above the current
    ///   price). 'out_of_they_money' will return options contracts that are out
    ///   of the money (call options with strike prices above the current price,
    ///   put options with strike prices below the current price).
